      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772716017510,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2. 分析维度\nQ: (bs, seqlen, heads, head_dim)\nK: (bs, cache_len + 1, heads, head_dim)\n\nQ: (bs, heads, seqlen, head_dim)\nK: (bs, heads, cache_len + 1, head_dim)\n\n对于一个bs的一个head:\n其中seqlen = 1\nsc = QKT = (1, head_dim) * (head_dim, cache_len + 1) = (1, cache_len + 1)\n\n\n3. 分配block\n对于独立变量分配不同block： 对于一个head分配一个block\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2. 分析维度\nQ: (bs, seqlen, heads, head_dim)\nK: (bs, cache_len + 1, heads, head_dim)\n\nQ: (bs, heads, seqlen, head_dim)\nK: (bs, heads, cache_len + 1, head_dim)\n\n对于一个bs的一个head:\n其中seqlen = 1\nsc = QKT = (1, head_dim) * (head_dim, cache_len + 1) = (1, cache_len + 1)\n\n\n3. 分配block\n对于独立变量分配不同block： 对于一个head分配一个block\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
